column18: 02/01/2016: Assailants threw a grenade at the house of Dorin Dragutanu in Chisinau, Moldova. Draguntanu, the National Bank of Moldova governor, was not harmed in the blast. No group claimed responsibility for the incident.
column108: A house was damaged in this attack.
